{
  "text": "MSC proliferation assays were performed using the Cell Counting Kit-8 (CCK-8; Dojindo Laboratories, Kumamoto, Japan) [CITATION_1] . Briefly, MSCs at passage 3 were seeded into 96-well plates (Thermo Scientific, Waltham, MA, USA) at a density of 1 \u00d7 10 3 cells/cm 2 , cultured in \u03b1-MEM medium with 10% FBS (6 wells in each group), added to CCK-8 solution at a ratio of 100 \u00b5L/\u00b5L, and incubated at 37\u00b0C for 1 h. Absorbance was then measured at a wavelength of 450 nm using a microplate reader (BMG LABTECH, Offenburg, Germany). In the current study, CCK-8 experiments were performed on days 1, 5, 7, 10, and 13.",
